The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

 Good Morning

 Hello It's Sunday, July 1, 2007

 Food Fight

 Enjoy Puchkaddict of Calcutta competition, presented by t2, at City Centre, 4pm to 8pm. 

 Evening Adda

 Be there at an evening of The Bong Connection adda and music at Tollygunge Club, 7.15pm.

 Smooth Moves

 Watch a foot-tapping dance performance by Sangvee Dance Centre, at Kala Mandir, 11am to 2pm.

 Eye on Art

 Browse through a painting exhibition by Subhash Pal at New South Gallery, Academy of Fine Arts, 3pm to 8pm. 

 Move on to Celebration of Nature, a show for World Environment Day at Artists Circle, 2pm to 7pm. 

 Stop over at Tribute to Humanity at Angan Art Gallery, 4pm to 8pm. 

 Check out works by Ekta Singha at Gallery Exposure, 54B Mahanirban Road, 3pm to 8pm. 




